| Feature     | Abstract Class                  | Interface                                   |
| ----------- | ------------------------------- | ------------------------------------------- |
| Methods     | Can be abstract or concrete     | Abstract by default; default/static allowed |
| Variables   | Instance variables allowed      | Only constants (static final)               |
| Inheritance | Single inheritance              | Multiple inheritance allowed                |
| Use case    | Common functionality + contract | Just a contract for classes                 |

